FBIS4-5557 "dreas070_c_94060" FBIS-EAS-94-070 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 North Korea Hwang Chang-yop, Social Scientists Return Hwang Chang-yop, Social Scientists Return SK1204051794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0428 GMT 12 Apr 94 SK1204051794 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 12 (KCNA) -- A delegation of Korean social scientists led by Hwang Chang-yop, secretary of the C.C., Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] and chairman of the Association of Korean Social Scientists, returned home on Monday after participating in the International Chuche Idea Seminar on Independence, Peace and Friendship held in India. It was met at the airport by Kim Yang-kon, vice-director of a department of the WPK Central Committee.
